Package sailpoint.workflow

Interface Summary
WorkflowHandler The interface of a class that can be registered to handle notifications of progress through a workflow.
 

Class Summary
AbstractWorkflowHandler Skeleton implementation of the WorkflowHandler class.
ApprovalLibrary  
BatchRequestLibrary Workflow library for processing batch requests
GroupLibrary Workflow library containing utilities for group management.
IdentityLibrary Workflow library containing utilities for identity management.
IdentityRequestLibrary A Collection of library method designed to handle the create, update and complete of an IdentityRequest object as it executes through a workflow.
IdentityRequestLibrary.RequestItemizer Utility class to help derive RequestItems from the ProvisioningPlan(s) that are passed into the workflow.
LCMLibrary Deprecated.
PolicyViolationLibrary A workflow library with methods related to policy violation workflows.
RoleLibrary A workflow library with methods related to role model approvals.
SAPGRCIntegrationLibrary  
StandardWorkflowHandler Default WorkflowHandler for most IdentityIQ workflows.
WorkflowContext Runtime information maintained by the workflow engine as it advances through a workflow case.
 

Enum Summary
StandardWorkflowHandler.EmailArgument Constants for WorkflowContext arguments when sending an email.
